channel.title: Homes Under the Hammer
channel.desc: Jacqui is in Westcliff-on-Sea in Essex to look at a two-bedroom maisonette, Martin is in Coleford, near the Forest of Dean, to see a flat in real need of renovation, and Dion is in Barlaston to see a three-bedroom end-of-terrace.
